## ğŸ“ Organization

### Documentation
All documentation is organized in `docs/`:
- `docs/guides/` - How-to guides and tutorials
- `docs/info/` - System information and inventories
- `docs/status/` - Current status reports
- `docs/integration/` - Integration documentation
- `docs/github/` - GitHub setup and troubleshooting
- `docs/cleanup/` - Cleanup and organization docs
- `docs/rebranding/` - Rebranding documentation
- `docs/tools/` - Tool documentation

See [docs/README.md](docs/README.md) for complete documentation index.

### OpenSpec
Change management system in `openspec/`:
- `openspec/AGENTS.md` - AI agent instructions
- `openspec/project.md` - Project definition
- `openspec/spec-kit/` - Specification management

See [openspec/README.md](openspec/README.md) for OpenSpec guide.

### Turbo Monorepo
- `turbo.json` - Monorepo build configuration
- `pnpm-workspace.yaml` - Workspace configuration

