## ğŸš€ Quick Start

### Setup
```bash
# Install dependencies
pnpm install

# Validate setup
pnpm run validate:setup

# Health check
pnpm run health:check
```

### Development
```bash
# Build all packages
pnpm run build

# Run development mode
pnpm run dev

# Type check
pnpm run type-check

# Lint
pnpm run lint
```

### Tools
```bash
# Generate system inventory
pnpm run inventory

# Consolidate documentation
pnpm run consolidate:docs

# System summary
pnpm run summary

# Check all
pnpm run check:all
```

### Independent Operation (After Cursor Updates)
```bash
# Auto-update after Cursor patches
pnpm run auto:update

# Quick maintenance
pnpm run maintain:quick

# Full maintenance
pnpm run maintain:full

# Apply patches
pnpm run apply:patches
```

### Health & Monitoring
```bash
# Health monitoring
pnpm run health:monitor        # Continuous monitoring
pnpm run health:monitor:once   # Single check

# Performance optimization
pnpm run optimize:performance

# Error recovery
pnpm run recover:auto
```

### Testing & Backups
```bash
# Automated testing
pnpm run test:run

# Backup management
pnpm run backup:create    # Create backup
pnpm run backup:list      # List backups
pnpm run backup:restore   # Restore backup
```

See [docs/INDEPENDENT_OPERATION.md](docs/INDEPENDENT_OPERATION.md) for complete guide.  
See [docs/IMPROVEMENTS_SUMMARY.md](docs/IMPROVEMENTS_SUMMARY.md) for latest improvements.

